name: now u see Me
description:
It's getting harder and harder to just be slutty online. Censorship from credit card companies is closing down porn sites left and right, and some of our favorite creators and creations are being erased. Now you see them, now you don't. Art is not meant to be censored.

Second in a short series on this subject. Source video by Me, of Me, run through a series of editors and apps. 2021. Thank you for listening.
